."},{"pid":"c4eb8c07f17b7b491d7e62b7de999fc9e5c66f72","tid":834581,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73cfa09afcd32ec32ef4df92ff4ee0d57eb6552b","tid":834581,"uid":109459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f04f95844684da18d9ebd0bcef876e0a80c69e1e","tid":834581,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c05d10807079ab00819247c10a10f1392da33073","tid":834581,"uid":109459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:40:01.000Z","msg":"交哂比公證行算吧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"巴打試過交哂比公證行嗎? <br />\n朋友個樓上都有肯見面討論點解決,唔想咁快行到呢步. 只係做備用方案.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"面對就－早整啦，有心要整就好易，業主們又唔係專業，私下解決都有好多伏位，揾公證行迫下就大家快Ｄ面對件事。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"都係. 有心整係好易, 但未有公證行經驗，想問下有搵過公證行經驗巴絲推介間公證行黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5410866de1f40763bda900ab562e02497849eb9f","tid":834581,"uid":109459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4eb8c07f17b7b491d7e62b7de999fc9e5c66f72","tid":834581,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73cfa09afcd32ec32ef4df92ff4ee0d57eb6552b","tid":834581,"uid":109459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f04f95844684da18d9ebd0bcef876e0a80c69e1e","tid":834581,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"巴打試過交哂比公證行嗎? <br />\n朋友個樓上都有肯見面討論點解決,唔想咁快行到呢步. 只係做備用方案.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"面對就－早整啦，有心要整就好易，業主們又唔係專業，私下解決都有好多伏位，揾公證行迫下就大家快Ｄ面對件事。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"都係. 有心整係好易, 但未有公證行經驗，想問下有搵過公證行經驗巴絲推介間公證行黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思我好多搵JO既經驗，多數都係廢，同埋佢地既報告係對業主無用的，見好多case比